ly-elected|title=Executive Board of Democratic Syria Assembly elected|date=13 December 2015|work=ANF Naws Desk|publisher=ANF News|accessdate=12 June 2016|agency=ANF|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220074139/http://anfenglish.com/kurdistan/executive-board-of-democratic-syria-assembly-elected|archive-date=2015-12-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 是[[北叙利亚民主联邦|北叙利亚民主联邦]]的一個行政区，原名'''舍赫巴地区'''，在由[[敘利亞民主力量|敘利亞民主力量]]解放自[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]後成立，位於[[科巴尼州|科巴尼州]]和[[阿夫林州|阿夫林州]]之間。

舍赫巴地區擁有自己的議會和參議院，分別在2016年1月28日及2016年2月2-4日兩次舍赫巴會議中成立。<ref name="Second conference of Shahba region">{{Cite web|url=http://cantonafrin.com/en/news/view/1658.a-delegation-from-the-democratic-administration-of-self-participate-in-the-second-conference-of-the-el--shahba-region.html|title=Delegation from the Democratic administration of Self-participate of self-participate in the first and second conference of the Shaba region|accessdate=12 June 2016|date=4 February 2016|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809175326/http://cantonafrin.com/en/news/view/1658.a-delegation-from-the-democratic-administration-of-self-participate-in-the-second-conference-of-the-el--shahba-region.html|archive-date=2016-08-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hawarnews.com/%D9%85%D8%AC%D9%84%D8%B3-%D8%A3%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%88%D8%B4%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%AE-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B7%D9%82-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D9%87%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D9%8A%D8%B5%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8/|title=Notables and tribal areas Shahba Council issued the final statement of its founding congress|date=2 February 2016|publisher=hawarnews.com|agency=ANHA|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624023143/http://www.hawarnews.com/%D9%85%D8%AC%D9%84%D8%B3-%D8%A3%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%88%D8%B4%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%AE-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B7%D9%82-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D9%87%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D9%8A%D8%B5%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8/|archivedate=2016年6月24日|df=}}</ref> 自治區政府則是在2016年3月22日建立。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://dckurd.org/2016/03/18/interview-with-ahmad-araj-member-of-the-political-commission-of-the-syrian-democratic-council/|title=Interview with Ahmad Araj Member of the Executive Committee of the Syrian Democratic Council|date=18 March 2016|work=dckurd.org|publisher=WKI|accessdate=12 June 2016|agency=WKI|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701004429/http://dckurd.org/2016/03/18/interview-with-ahmad-araj-member-of-the-political-commission-of-the-syrian-democratic-council/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

舍赫巴地區議會在[[叙利亚民主委员会|叙利亚民主委员会]]上有直接的代表席位，席汗·傑多也是被選出在委员会中代表舍赫巴地區的委員<ref name="ANF News">{{Cite news|url=http://anfenglish.com/kurdistan/executive-board-of-democratic-syria-assembly-elected|title=Executive Board of Democratic Syria Assembly elected|date=13 December 2015|work=ANF Naws Desk|publisher=ANF News|accessdate=12 June 2016|agency=ANF|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220074139/http://anfenglish.com/kurdistan/executive-board-of-democratic-syria-assembly-elected|archive-date=2015-12-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

目前，[[曼比季|曼比季]]和Tell Rifaat分别是该地区东部和西部的行政中心。

== 地理 ==
[[File:De_facto_cantons_of_Rojava.png|左]]（橙）、[[科巴尼州|科巴尼州]]（红）、舍赫巴地区（紫）和[[賈茲拉州|賈茲拉州]]（绿）。]]
舍赫巴地區目前擁有[[曼比季|曼比季]]周圍、迪什林和艾琳瑪等內戰前屬於[[阿勒頗省|阿勒頗省]]的大片區域，由[[敘利亞民主力量|敘利亞民主力量]]控制。

== 歷史 ==
{{模板:羅賈瓦政治}}
2012年7月，原先敘利亞政府控制的地區大部分被[[人民保护部队|人民保护部队]](YPG)等反對派佔領。

2014年1月，[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]發動大規模的攻勢，控制了從[[曼比季|曼比季]]到[[達比克|達比克]]整片區域。

2015年12月敘利亞民主力量(SDF)發起攻勢，奪回了戰略要點迪什林水壩和周圍的村莊, 在幼發拉底河西岸形成一個小的突出部。接著幾個月預備解放曼比季市的行動，因為土耳其政府的干涉而延後。

2016年5月[[曼比季攻勢|曼比季攻勢]]終於從3個軸線發起，包括沿著[[幼發拉底河|幼發拉底河]]河岸的南北兩側，以及往曼比季市的南郊，試圖切斷拉卡-曼比季公路。<ref name="launch offensive">{{Cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-offensive-idUSKCN0YN377|title=Exclusive: U.S.-backed Syria forces launch offensive for Manbij pocket - U.S. officials|accessdate=6 June 2016|date=1 June 2016|publisher=|via=Reuters|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412184735/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-offensive-idUSKCN0YN377|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年5月30日到6月12日的[[曼比季攻勢|曼比季攻勢]]從伊斯蘭國中解放了超過100座村莊，並建立了舍赫巴州。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/2016/06/11/47283|title=The Syria Democratic Forces reach 16 kilometers in the western countryside of Manbij and control about 100 villages.|date=11 June 2016|work=SOHR|access-date=2016-07-06|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510132035/https://www.syriahr.com/en/4049/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

